<article class="article-content">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

  <p>PawPicks UK (pawpicks.co.uk) is a static website with no user accounts, no contact forms, and no advertising. We take privacy seriously — and the best way to protect your privacy is to collect as little data as possible. So we don't.</p>

  <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>

  <p><strong>First-party data: None.</strong></p>

  <p>We do not use analytics software. We do not use tracking pixels. We do not set any cookies ourselves. We have no newsletter sign-up. We have no user accounts.</p>

  <p>If you visit this site and do nothing but read, we have no record of your visit.</p>

  <h2>Hosting</h2>

  <p>PawPicks UK is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may process certain technical information as part of delivering the site to you — such as your IP address and browser type — in order to route and serve web requests. This is standard infrastructure processing.</p>

  <p>Cloudflare's privacy policy is available at <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/en-gb/privacypolicy/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Affiliate Links and Third-Party Cookies</h2>

  <p>This site contains affiliate links to Amazon UK. If you click one of those links, you will be taken to Amazon's website, and Amazon may set cookies on your device.</p>

  <p>Those cookies are Amazon's responsibility, not ours. Amazon's privacy policy applies once you're on their site. You can read it at <a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">amazon.co.uk/privacy</a>.</p>

  <p>We have no access to or control over cookies set by Amazon or any other third-party site we link to.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights Under UK GDPR</h2>

  <p>Under UK GDPR, you have rights including the right to access, rectify, or erase personal data we hold about you. Since we hold no personal data about you, there is nothing to access, rectify, or erase.</p>

  <p>If you believe we have collected personal data about you in error, contact us at <strong>hello@pawpicks.co.uk</strong> and we'll investigate promptly.</p>

  <h2>Links to Other Websites</h2>

  <p>Our reviews link to external sites (primarily Amazon UK, and occasionally brand websites). Once you leave PawPicks, this privacy policy no longer applies. We recommend reading the privacy policy of any site you visit.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>

  <p>Questions about this privacy policy? Email us at <strong>hello@pawpicks.co.uk</strong>.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>

  <p>If we materially change how we handle data, we'll update this page and change the "last updated" date at the top. We don't anticipate significant changes — we plan to remain a simple, tracking-free static site.</p>
</article>
